@page "/solutions/sales"
@layout MarketingLayout

<PageTitle>NavTour for Sales — Personalized Demos That Close Deals</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="Send prospects a custom demo minutes after a discovery call. AI personalizes every experience with their company name, data, and use case." />
</HeadContent>

<HeroSection Eyebrow="For Sales Teams"
             Title="Generic slide decks don't close deals. Personalized demos do."
             Subtitle="Send prospects a custom demo minutes after a discovery call. AI personalizes every experience with their company name, data, and use case."
             PrimaryCtaText="Start Building Free"
             SecondaryCtaText="See Sales Demos"
             SecondaryCtaUrl="/contact" />

@* Pain Points *@
<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-3 reveal-stagger">
            <div class="mkt-card">
                <h3>Every discovery call ends the same way</h3>
                <p>You promise to send a follow-up. Then you spend 2 hours building a custom slide deck that the prospect may never open.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-card">
                <h3>Champions can't resell internally</h3>
                <p>Your contact loved the demo, but they can't recreate it for their VP. The deal stalls in committee.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-card">
                <h3>No insight into deal engagement</h3>
                <p>You don't know if the prospect watched your recording, forwarded the deck, or ghosted you entirely.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Solution Feature 1 *@
<section class="mkt-section-alt">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">Personalize</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Personalized Demos in 60 Seconds</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">AI generates a prospect-specific demo from your template library. Company name, logo, industry data — all swapped automatically. Send a demo link before the discovery call even ends.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">AI personalizing a demo in real time</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Solution Feature 2 *@
<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Champion sharing demo with buying committee</div>
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">Enable</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Champion Enablement Assets</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Give your champion a demo they can share internally. It walks their VP through the value prop, highlights the relevant use case, and captures engagement from every stakeholder who views it.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Solution Feature 3 *@
<section class="mkt-section-alt">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">Intelligence</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Deal Intelligence</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">AI tracks who viewed your demo, how long they spent, which features they explored, and whether they shared it. Intent scoring tells you which deals to prioritize and when to follow up.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Deal intelligence dashboard with intent scores</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Metrics *@
<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container text-center reveal">
        <h2>Sales teams using NavTour see results</h2>
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-3" style="margin-top:var(--space-10)">
            <MetricCard Value="2.4x" Label="faster deal velocity" />
            <MetricCard Value="40%" Label="higher win rate with personalized demos" />
            <MetricCard Value="73%" Label="of demos are shared with 2+ stakeholders" />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<CtaSection Dark="true"
            Title="Close deals faster with AI-personalized demos"
            Subtitle="Start free. Send your first personalized demo today." />
